author: xsteve
msg: Better support for giving an answer to the certificate validity question
(svn-process-filter): Find out, if the certificate validity question
is asked. If yes, ask the user whether he wants to accept the certificate.

author: lgo
msg: Small fixes in the crash handler code after review by malcolm.
We are not going to support UNICODE builds ...
(get_temp_filename): ... so no need  to use GetTempPathA explicitly. Reserve
some more place (64 chars) in the buffer for the filename.
(write_stacktrace): error out in preprocessor when building a 64bit
executable, tell the user how to disable the whole crash handler. Cleanup
